# Source constraint for astroai-lab, consumed by `make lock-astroai-lab`.
#
# Pin is a fixed commit SHA, NOT a git tag and NOT a package version.
# The `v0.1.0` tag still declares the legacy `name = "canfar-lab"` metadata;
# the rename to `name = "astroai-lab"` happened post-v0.1.0 (commit 5f269b7
# onward). Pin to a SHA so reproducibility is git-pinned not version-pinned.
